355
00:29:37,080 --> 00:29:38,360
Kakak di sini, 'kan?

356
00:29:39,480 --> 00:29:40,680
Ya.

357
00:29:41,600 --> 00:29:42,800
Ya, kakak di sini.

358
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:47,760
Rasanya memang canggung karena Kakak tidak terlihat.

359
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:49,840
Tapi seru juga.

360
00:29:51,040 --> 00:29:52,240
Aku juga.

361
00:29:54,280 --> 00:29:56,000
Sebaiknya kita membuat aturan.

362
00:29:57,120 --> 00:30:00,760
Saat duduk di meja makan, Kakak duduk di seberangku,

363
00:30:01,120 --> 00:30:04,040
dan saat berjalan atau duduk berdampingan,

364
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:06,120
Kakak di sebelah kanan.

365
00:30:07,280 --> 00:30:08,480
Bagaimana?

366
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:13,160
Boleh.

367
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:17,400
Kalau begitu, sepakat, ya?

368
00:30:17,920 --> 00:30:20,400
Ya, sepakat.

369
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:22,600
"Voucher Perjalanan Bebas"

370
00:30:23,280 --> 00:30:24,880
Silakan pindah ke lokasi yang Kakak inginkan.

371
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:30,080
Bagaimana kalau ke Amerika? Kakak dulu ingin ke Amerika, 'kan?

372
00:30:32,520 --> 00:30:34,000
Kakak tidak mau ke Amerika.

373
00:30:38,080 --> 00:30:39,400
Kakak ingin berada di sisimu.

374
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:43,800
Es krim terfavorit Han So Hyun.

375
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:51,080
Enak?

376
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:57,000
Aku mau mandi dulu.

377
00:31:18,720 --> 00:31:22,320
Aku tidak bisa menonton TV atau bermain Monopoli.

378
00:31:23,440 --> 00:31:25,160
Namun, Na Hyun

379
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:30,040
