380
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:34,560
Padahal dia tidak perlu bersusah payah seperti itu.

381
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:39,160
Na Hyun merasa terbebani karena aku.

382
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:41,920
